divs: Sighting Detailsit was 2 in the morning,on the deerfield beach pier,i was fishing and i looked to my left whitch is north and i saw this object comming toward me and what was unusual was is was totally silent and no lights were anywhere on the object,it made a wooshing ,almost like wind sound,had no idea what it was but knew it was very stange,it was about 70 feet above my head and it was going north to south along the coast of the beach.i cant exactly describe it but it was like a triangular,box like all back,it was night though.and made a noise as it passed overhead and the only thing i can describe as shhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh and floated right passed me.there was an old black lady who was next to me and i said holy shit did you see that,i couldnt explain the feeling i had like i was in total disbelief,shock and amazmentshe looked at me and made the strangest laugh.like i was crazy.and at the same time she knew i was right like this wasnt her first time,i saw it just float south down the coast and that was it.i told everyone i knew and everyone thought i was nuts,but dammit i know what i saw.it still is with me today,even the feelin i had that night.
Summary: watched ufo come frome the north and head south
